reviewText: Not my style.  Tara speaks too quickly and moves through the routine too fast.  Also $70 for 3 short, poorly taught routines?  Waste of money.
great set of yoga videos been using them every day!
I really like all the different workouts that you can choose with this DVD set. I do this at least three times a week!
Easy to follow.  Gentle for beginners.  Varying degrees of workout are great.  Really enjoying it at all times of the day.
